title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 3 categories of Response on the x axis representing 4 groups: Under $50, $50 - $100, $100 - $200, and $200 and up.
Averaging these 4 groups, the highest category is found for Response BlackBerry owners with a mean value of 23.5.
Followed by iPhone owners with a mean value of 23.5.
The lowest category is observed at Android owners that has a mean value of 23.25

In case of Android owners, Under $50 shows more dominance than any other Response and it has the lowest value in iPhone owners. On the other hand, group $200 and up is highest in case of iPhone owners and has minimum impact for Response BlackBerry owners.
